{"tid":1677811,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解唔多區攪大型商場和平集會？","createTime":"2019-10-27T10:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T16:38:16.000Z","uid":76310,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d56afe4c736f9d507e3898f71400a77b82ea1487","tid":1677811,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"如果有魔警唔比人比大型商場，封晒d路，唔比人入商場<br />\n咪唔好入<br />\n或者有人係商場聚集魔警就入商場捉同圍捕，咪由佢咁做<br />\n如果佢由大家入商場，咪商場集會<br />\n只要唔標籤自己，例如黑衫同口罩，佢鬼知要目標捉邊個<br />\n如果魔警唔理，可以由和平集會變裝修大會，如果魔警見商場既人就捉，睇下有冇人去商場幫襯。或者可以攪到多區商場關門<br />\n<br />\n好過去某個地點，未開始已經封路，各路口都便衣睇水，邊個去就拉邊個<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"477c2e0ab1130c10cc9877861fe96f13eeef85bb","tid":1677811,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"0b102fd3f1c53f42ac5966124d4163687cc9d632","tid":1677811,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb067b6006fbb685ba8115d20bcd68087cfb774a","tid":1677811,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3723953e50e780eb3f25ed2d5f271c70241a3c","tid":1677811,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"289d304544770cfd28543486d874ebe192c8e3d2","tid":1677811,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019